01:40:54,710 --> 01:40:57,050
Anh hiểu rồi

1580
01:40:57,210 --> 01:40:59,510
Anh sẽ không bao giờ rời bỏ em

1581
01:41:23,780 --> 01:41:26,120
<i>At first I was afraid, I was petrified</i>

1582
01:41:26,280 --> 01:41:29,830
<i>Kept thinking I could never live</i>
<i>Without you by my side</i>

1583
01:41:30,000 --> 01:41:33,710
<i>Then I spent so many nights</i>
<i>Thinking how you did me wrong</i>

1584
01:41:33,870 --> 01:41:37,460
<i>And I grew strong</i>
<i>And I learned how to get along</i>

